column2: Amber Heard is abusive.
column26: For Johnny Depp to keep his job as grindelwald
column33: Warner Brothers: For Johnny Depp to keep his job as grindelwald
column34:
Even though there was plenty of evidence to show he was the victim of domestic abuse he loses his job as Grindelwald. He may have lost the court case about defamation but it has been proven in videos that he was the actual victim of abuse not Amber Heard.

What does this say to all the men who are currently being abused by their partners? They’ll see a man who has gone through abuse and it caused him to basically be ostracised from Hollywood. 

Instead of supporting a man who has gone through so much, including getting part of his finger cut off, Warner studios decided to sack him, as if he has not been through enough! 

This petition is to try and attempt to get Warner Brothers to recast Johnny Depp, as we need to support people who have been through abuse. If Warner Brothers show their support for Johnny Depp it would hopefully encourage other men who get abused to come forward!

1. The perjury of one PROVEN abuser & liar.
2. A story in a tabloid you wouldn’t use to line a cat box.
3. One corrupt and/or compromised judge. 
Terrifying and shameful, this is spitting in the face of true victims of violence. There are MILLIONS of us worldwide fighting for justice. Amber Heard belongs in prison. Johnny Depp deserves SO MUCH better than this.
